  "id": "api/core/switch",
  "title": "@switch",
  "contents": "<article>\n  <div class=\"breadcrumb-container\">\n    <div class=\"breadcrumb\">\n      <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n        {\n          \"@context\": \"http://schema.org\",\n          \"@type\": \"BreadcrumbList\",\n          \"itemListElement\": [\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 1, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api\", \"name\": \"API\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 2, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/core\", \"name\": \"@angular/core\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 3, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/core/switch\", \"name\": \"@switch\" } }\n          ]\n        }\n      </script>\n        <a href=\"/api\">API</a> > <a href=\"api/core\">@angular/core</a>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular/tree/17.3.12/aio/content/blocks/core/switch.md\" aria-label=\"View Source\" title=\"View Source\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n  </div>\n  <header class=\"api-header\">\n    <h1 id=\"switch\">@switch<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/switch#switch\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n    <label class=\"api-type-label block\">block</label>\n  </header>\n  <aio-toc class=\"embedded\"></aio-toc>\n\n  <div class=\"api-body\">\n  <section class=\"short-description\">\n    <p>The <code><a href=\"api/core/switch\" class=\"code-anchor\">@switch</a></code> block is inspired by the JavaScript <code>switch</code> statement:</p>\n\n    <p><a href=\"api/core/switch#description\">See more...</a></p>\n  </section>\n  \n    <h2 id=\"syntax\">Syntax<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/switch#syntax\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n    <code-example language=\"html\">\n@switch (condition) {\n  @case (caseA) {\n    Case A.\n  }\n  @case (caseB) {\n    Case B.\n  }\n  @default {\n    Default case.\n  }\n}\n</code-example>\n\n  \n\n  \n<section class=\"description\">\n  <h2 id=\"description\">Description<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/switch#description\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <p>The <code><a href=\"api/core/switch\" class=\"code-anchor\">@switch</a></code> blocks displays content selected by one of the cases matching against the conditional expression. The value of the conditional expression is compared to the case expression using the <code>===</code> operator.</p>\n<p>The <code>@default</code> block is optional and can be omitted. If no <code>@case</code> matches the expression and there is no <code>@default</code> block, nothing is shown.</p>\n<p><strong><code><a href=\"api/core/switch\" class=\"code-anchor\">@switch</a></code> does not have fallthrough</strong>, so you do not need an equivalent to a <code>break</code> or <code>return</code> statement.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - guide/control_flow\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - /api\n - api/core\n - api/core/switch#description\n - api/core/switch#switch\n - api/core/switch#syntax\n - https://github.com/angular/angular/tree/17.3.12/aio/content/blocks/core/switch.md\n-->"
}